the Buddha called this constant maintenance dukkha

139
00:06:37,375 --> 00:06:39,166
commonly translated as suffering

140
00:06:39,500 --> 00:06:42,750
but it's more like a persistent unease

141
00:06:42,958 --> 00:06:46,333
a background anxiety that never fully goes away

142
00:06:46,333 --> 00:06:48,125
as long as there's a you to protect

143
00:06:48,583 --> 00:06:50,791
so what happens when this self disappears

144
00:06:51,125 --> 00:06:52,208
freedom happens

