like putting down a heavy backpack

159
00:07:36,500 --> 00:07:38,500
I didn't even realize I was carrying

160
00:07:39,541 --> 00:07:41,833
this is what the Buddha was pointing to

161
00:07:41,916 --> 00:07:43,416
when the self disappears

162
00:07:43,458 --> 00:07:45,916
the constant inner critic finally shuts up

163
00:07:45,916 --> 00:07:47,875
because there's no you to criticize

164
00:07:48,250 --> 00:07:49,958
embarrassment fades away

165
00:07:50,083 --> 00:07:52,416
because there's no reputation to protect

166
00:07:52,750 --> 00:07:54,750
the need to be special vanishes

167
00:07:55,083 --> 00:07:57,416
because there's no you that needs to stand out

