too studies of experienced meditators

181
00:08:36,125 --> 00:08:38,375
show reduced activity in the areas of the brain

182
00:08:38,375 --> 00:08:40,541
associated with self referential thinking

183
00:08:40,791 --> 00:08:41,500
and increased

184
00:08:41,500 --> 00:08:44,041
activity in areas associated with awareness

185
00:08:44,041 --> 00:08:45,750
and present moment attention

186
00:08:46,375 --> 00:08:49,708
in other words as the self construct weakens

187
00:08:50,083 --> 00:08:51,958
awareness actually expands

188
00:08:53,250 --> 00:08:54,875
but here's an important point

189
00:08:54,916 --> 00:08:55,250
this

190
00:08:55,250 --> 00:08:57,458
freedom doesn't mean you become an emotional zombie

191
00:08:57,458 --> 00:08:59,000
or lose your personality

192
00:08:59,250 --> 00:09:01,875
actually quite the opposite

193
00:09:02,375 --> 00:09:04,083
when you're not constantly maintaining

194
00:09:04,083 --> 00:09:07,791
a rigid sense of self you become more spontaneous

