00:10:10,916 --> 00:10:12,625
were suddenly not so solid

217
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:14,666
when non self is realized

218
00:10:14,666 --> 00:10:17,250
relationships transform in remarkable ways

219
00:10:17,583 --> 00:10:18,916
as the Buddha taught

220
00:10:26,833 --> 00:10:30,250
first comparison and competition naturally fade away

221
00:10:30,500 --> 00:10:33,125
when there's no solid you to compare with others

222
00:10:33,708 --> 00:10:36,250
the exhausting game of one-upmanship ends

223
00:10:36,791 --> 00:10:38,708
