224
00:10:38,791 --> 00:10:40,375
smarter wealthier

225
00:10:40,375 --> 00:10:42,000
or more successful than others

226
00:10:42,708 --> 00:10:45,708
because there's no separate you that needs to win

227
00:10:46,500 --> 00:10:48,416
Jason a longtime meditator

