237
00:11:12,708 --> 00:11:14,958
without the barrier of a separate self

238
00:11:15,166 --> 00:11:17,750
you directly experience others joy and suffering

239
00:11:17,750 --> 00:11:19,416
as not separate from your own

240
00:11:19,916 --> 00:11:21,958
compassion becomes less of an effort

241
00:11:22,083 --> 00:11:24,083
and more of a natural response

