00:11:25,166 --> 00:11:27,375
the Dalai Lama explains it this way

243
00:11:35,708 --> 00:11:38,500
third relationships become less needy

244
00:11:38,750 --> 00:11:40,041
when you're not looking to others

245
00:11:40,041 --> 00:11:41,541
to complete your sense of self

