00:25:20,791 --> 00:25:23,291
and would love to hear about your experiences

541
00:25:24,833 --> 00:25:28,083
and remember the next time you find yourself stressed

542
00:25:28,083 --> 00:25:30,166
anxious or caught in self concern

543
00:25:30,416 --> 00:25:31,958
just pause and ask yourself

544
00:25:32,500 --> 00:25:34,125
what happens when I don't exist

545
00:25:34,916 --> 00:25:36,708
you might be surprised at the freedom

546
00:25:36,708 --> 00:25:38,208
that question opens up

